{"tid":192002,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打中意聽葉振棠?","createTime":"2017-04-08T09:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T02:21:32.000Z","uid":104053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48528cff98fac0bc8d5d9ea82e3225441b6091be","tid":192002,"uid":104053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"見好似冇咩人提起，唔知呢度有冇同好?<br />\n其實好多主題曲同插曲都係棠哥唱<br />\n<br />\n抒情有忘盡心中情、找不著藉口、笛子姑娘、月亮神 (後兩首唔係電視劇歌)<br />\n古裝主題曲就有太極張三豐、大內群英等等<br />\n勵志就勝利雙手創、世界由我做、信心<br />\n<br />\n希望可以拋磚引玉啦"},{"pid":"b49e4bd6e66b6e5a41e9cba762820f24d825dadf","tid":192002,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"醉凡塵 <br />\n<br />\n一個信念<br />\n<br />\n誰為正邪定分界<br />\n<br />\n忘盡心中情"},{"pid":"2e80ed15ecdb1cd76b855b77651dbbc0108dfd05","tid":192002,"uid":104053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醉凡塵 <br />\n<br />\n一個信念<br />\n<br />\n誰為正邪定分界<br />\n<br />\n忘盡心中情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個信念係南海十三郎主題曲，好歌! 可惜少人識<br />\n難為正邪定分界係經典中的經典"},{"pid":"26810aca11ca153ec9de04eb59277fb982ec67d9","tid":192002,"uid":104053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5d4104cd7e2efa9f7a3f4a374a6a4e27978a7f","tid":192002,"uid":7811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"係中國搭旅遊巴成日被逼聽呢條友嘅演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8fa0ad288767bc13be1d54eefe85256a3a0425","tid":192002,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係中國搭旅遊巴成日被逼聽呢條友嘅演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計 岩班大叔聽"},{"pid":"6be61e6b7d649d487ce334d3e8eec5ff030d6d19","tid":192002,"uid":104053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":